@using VedAstro.Library
@attribute [Route(PageRoute.Donate)]

<PageTitle>Donate</PageTitle>

<PageTop Title="Support us" IconName="iconoir:donate">
    <Description>With every donation you'll receive free astro gifts as a sign of our thanks</Description>
</PageTop>


<div class="d-flex flex-wrap">
    @*KO-FI WIDGET*@
    <div class="me-5" style="">
        <iframe id='kofiframe' src='https://ko-fi.com/vedastro/?hidefeed=true&widget=true&embed=true&preview=true' style="width: @GR.W412px; height: 557px;" class="border shadow rounded-4" title='vedastro'></iframe>
    </div>

    @*STACK BOXES ON RIGHT*@
    <div>
        <div class="gap-3">
            <p>
                Free Gifts:
            </p>
            <InfoBox MaxWidth="365" FullWidth="@true" Title="Full Life Chart" Description="Written full life analysis by expert astrologer" IconName="icon-park:table-report"/>
            <InfoBox MaxWidth="365" FullWidth="@true" Title="Astrologer Call" Description="45 minute live call consultation with vedic astrologer" IconName="flat-color-icons:customer-support"/>
            <InfoBox MaxWidth="365" Color="success" FullWidth="@true" Title="Monthly Updates" Description="We'll keep you updated on latest astro events" IconName="emojione:closed-mailbox-with-raised-flag"/>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<hr/>


<div style="max-width:@GR.W667px;">
    <h4 class="fw-bold">Why Donate?</h4>
    <p class="text-justify" >
        Donations help to run the web servers 24/7 &amp; to continually improve the project.
    </p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">Transparent Donations</h4>
    <p class="text-justify">
        Know exactly where your money is going.
        We try to keep the fund flow as transparent as possible.
        That's why you can choose to sponsor a specific thing
        like domain fees or hosting costs. Leave your choice in the message box.
    </p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold"><Icon IconName="emojione:convenience-store" /> Hosting Costs</h4>
    <p class="text-justify">
        @*<Icon IconName="emojione:convenience-store" />*@
        1st priority goes to hosting costs. Currently VedAstro is hosted in Microsoft Azure
        as a Static Web App which reduces running costs, but it comes with minor reliability issues.
        With support from users we hope to diversify the hosting platform for stable & reliable service anywhere in the world.
    </p>

    <h4 class="fw-bold">Programmer Costs</h4>
    <p class="text-justify">
        As of December 2022 more than <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/VedAstro/VedAstro/discussions/4" class="link-primary fw-bold">88,000 lines of code</a> was written for this project not including documentation.
        That's an impressive number. The more code there is, the more testing &amp; debugging that needs to be done. As such more developer/programmer work hours are required.
        Your donations go a long way to help pay for this expenses.
    </p>

</div>
